	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sneak decreases the aggro radius of Mobs towards you.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you see a ready to attack, and sneak, he will still attack you if you get within his reduced aggro radius him.<br><br>The only real use I have found for sneak is selling to merchants.  For any other use, I found it just as easy to run where I'm wanting to go and use feign death to shake those aggroed mobs off me.  Maybe in the higher levels where FD doesn't work as well, sneak might be preferred, but I kinda doubt it.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
