	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>An often-overlooked magic 1HB weapon is the darkwood staff.&nbsp;&nbsp;You can often buy a lambent stone for as little as 20 pp.  In the Temple of Solusek Ro, Romar Sunto will give you a darkwood staff in return for a lambent stone.  This is a 5/28 magic stick that may well be the cheapest magic 1HB you can find.<br><br>For 2HB up to level 20 or so, I can't think of anything to touch a Runed Totem Staff for quality and price.  With a 9/37 damage/delay ratio and +5 HP (and +5 mana, but monks don't care), it's a bargain, and I've bought several for 4-10 pp.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
