	   <tr><td colspan=2>Also worthy of noting that for those of us who are forced to or enjoy going overweight with our monks, having hard AC rather than AGI modified AC reduces our penalty a bit.&nbsp;&nbsp;We still lose out, but not as significantly as if we followed Verant's advice and made AGI our primary stat for monks.<br><br>My human monk had points put into STR, AGI, DEX, and STA (this was long before any of the debates over the purpose of stats), and my iksar monk had all 20 points put into STR.  My Iksar does a few points more in damage than my human monk did in the same level range...probably not enough to worry, but once I outfit my iksar with some STR enhancing gear, it should be very noticeable<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
